{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838990217,"sessionID":"ses_287c1b50dffefEaM28w6W6Q2TH","part":{"id":"prt_d78408e59001a83tUHnMiCfCTU","messageID":"msg_d783ea81d0015n5Jy67Hf3jNBS","sessionID":"ses_287c1b50dffefEaM28w6W6Q2TH","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-a1fe2c42f9c0459b9bfd87f009e3fcf0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# pkg/apis — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition Design\n\n## AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n**Module**: `pkg/apis`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Purpose**: Define Kubernetes CRDs for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter resources, enable client-go generation, and provide type-safe API access.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Package Structure\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n├── runtime/\n│   └── v1alpha1/\n│       ├── agentruntime_types.go   # AgentRuntime spec/status\n│       ├── codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter spec/status\n│       ├── doc.go                   # Package documentation\n│       ├── groupversion_info.go     # GroupVersion constants\n│       ├── register.go              # Scheme registration\n│       └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go # DeepCopy methods (controller-gen)\nclient-go/                          # Generated client library\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/                   # Generated types (symlink or copy)\n```\n\n### API Group\n\n- **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n- **Scope**: `Namespaced`\n\n### Component Interactions\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    Kubernetes API Server                │\n│                                                          │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │         runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1    │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │  agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh │  │  │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │  codeinterpreters.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh││  │\n│  │  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                          │\n                          │ k8s client-go\n                          ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                 client-go (Generated)                   │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/     │  │\n│  │    • AgentRuntimeInterface                       │  │\n│  │    • CodeInterpreterInterface                    │  │\n│  │    • REST CRUD + Watch                           │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/    │  │\n│  │    • AgentRuntimeInformer                        │  │\n│  │    • CodeInterpreterInformer                     │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │  listers/runtime/v1alpha1/                      │  │\n│  │    • AgentRuntimeLister                          │  │\n│  │    • CodeInterpreterLister                       │  │\n│  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n## Data Structures\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go`\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimeSpec defines the desired state of AgentRuntime\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    // MaxSessionDuration is the maximum duration for any session\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration string `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"`\n    \n    // SessionTimeout is the idle timeout before a session is terminated\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout string `json:\"sessionTimeout\"`\n    \n    // TargetPort specifies the HTTP/HTTPS ports to expose\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:MinItems=1\n    TargetPort []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n    \n    // PodTemplate defines the pod template for agent sandbox pods\n    PodTemplate PodTemplateSpec `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n}\n\n// AgentRuntimeStatus defines the observed state of AgentRuntime\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    // Conditions represent the latest available observations\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // ObservedGeneration is the most recent generation observed\n    ObservedGeneration int64 `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// TargetPort defines a single HTTP/HTTPS port target\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    // Port is the port number\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=1\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Maximum=65535\n    Port int32 `json:\"port\"`\n    \n    // Protocol must be \"HTTP\" or \"HTTPS\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n    Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n    \n    // Name is an optional name for the port\n    Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // PathPrefix is the URL path prefix for this port\n    PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// PodTemplateSpec defines the pod template specification\ntype PodTemplateSpec struct {\n    // Metadata for the pod\n    Metadata metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // Spec for the pod\n    Spec PodSpec `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// AgentRuntime is the Schema for the agentruntimes API\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:shortName=art\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    \n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec,omitempty\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// AgentRuntimeList contains a list of AgentRuntime\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    \n    Items []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### CodeInterpreter\n\n**File**: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n\n```go\n// CodeInterpreterSpec defines the desired state of CodeInterpreter\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    // AuthMode specifies the authentication mode\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n    AuthMode string `json:\"authMode\"`\n    \n    // MaxSessionDuration is the maximum duration for any session\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration string `json:\"maxSessionDuration\"`\n    \n    // SessionTimeout is the idle timeout before a session is terminated\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout string `json:\"sessionTimeout\"`\n    \n    // Ports specifies the HTTP/HTTPS ports to expose\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:MinItems=1\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports\"`\n    \n    // Template defines the pod template for code interpreter pods\n    Template InterpreterTemplateSpec `json:\"template\"`\n    \n    // WarmPoolSize is the size of the warm pool\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Minimum=0\n    WarmPoolSize int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n}\n\n// CodeInterpreterStatus defines the observed state of CodeInterpreter\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    // Conditions represent the latest available observations\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // Ready indicates the code interpreter is ready\n    Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n    \n    // ObservedGeneration is the most recent generation observed\n    ObservedGeneration int64 `json:\"observedGeneration,omitempty\"`\n}\n